12
00:00:55,088 --> 00:00:56,723
<i>There are no words to describe</i>

13
00:00:56,756 --> 00:00:58,625
<i>how I feel inside</i>

14
00:00:58,625 --> 00:01:01,995
<i>I'm really really stuck</i>
<i>on you whoa, whoa!</i>

15
00:01:02,062 --> 00:01:03,630
